name: A Reverie

reviews.review_text:
An incredible experience of taste, rich of flavors.
The ambiance of the place is great but the food is even better. A lot of effort is also put on the presentation of the meals. No details are left appart. This is second time I visit this place in less than one year but they kept their standard at the same ultimate level. Impressive !
The price is incredibly humble compared to the high quality.
They would deserve at least one star at Michelin.
Definitely the restaurant to visit when in Goa !

It is a cozy spot with a very aesthetic vibe :-)

We tried their Red Sauce Pasta and Lebanese platter, both of which were incredibly flavorful. The pasta was a standout.

Their cocktail menu is impressive, and the Lemon Ice is a refreshing must-try.

While the portion sizes might be smaller than expected, the quality of the food more than makes up for it.

Great ambience and an interesting menu, but food portions and taste do not match the menu description or the price. Service is slow. The pastas are average. Most shockingly, for a place serving Italian food, they're out of stock for bread.

description:
### A Reverie: A Culinary Delicacy in Corlim Ind. Estate

Nestled in the vibrant Corlim Industrial Estate, A Reverie boasts an impressive 4.6-star rating from over 2,800 enthusiastic patrons, making it a must-visit spot in Goa. This fine dining establishment has garnered praise for its delicious offerings and inviting atmosphere, underscored by customer feedback that frequently highlights its exquisite *ambience*, flavorful *fine dining* menu, and proximity to a serene *beach*.

### Ambiance & Design

A Reverie's ambiance is characterized by a cozy yet sophisticated aesthetic, reminiscent of a chic beachside escape. Customers describe it as "very aesthetic," where every detail contributes to an inviting atmosphere. The warm lighting and tasteful décor create a relaxed setting, ideal for enjoying a meal with friends or that special someone. The restaurant cleverly merges modern design with local artistic touches, as evident in the compelling photographs shared by guests which capture the elegantly set tables and thoughtfully selected furnishings.

### Menu & Culinary Experience

The culinary offerings at A Reverie are equally noteworthy, with a menu that sparks excitement and pleasure. Guests rave about the **Red Sauce Pasta** and an **authentic Lebanese platter**, both acclaimed for their rich flavors. The attention to detail in food presentation is remarkable; patrons have highlighted how “no details are left apart.” Signature drinks like the **Lemon Ice cocktail** add a refreshing twist, making it an ideal choice for those hot Goan afternoons. While some guests have pointed out that portion sizes might be on the smaller side, the consensus is that the quality of the food is worth every penny. The restaurant’s commitment to maintaining high standards is evident, with many customers urging that they deserve a Michelin star for their remarkable culinary prowess.

### Customer Experience & Service

A Reverie’s customer service has drawn mixed responses; while many describe the staff as friendly and accommodating, others have mentioned that the service can be slow at times. Patrons appreciate the overall demeanor of the staff who strive to ensure a pleasant dining experience. There’s also a hint of disappointment with certain menu items, such as a notable shortage of bread, which can detract from the ambiance of an Italian dining experience. Nonetheless, the restaurant’s welcoming atmosphere encourages guests to relax and enjoy their meals at their own pace.

### Popularity & Reviews

A reverie has effectively established itself as a popular dining destination, with glowing customer sentiment heard across social media platforms. Several diners commend the restaurant for its combination of top-notch dining and modest pricing, asserting that it is the place to be when visiting Goa. It’s evident from reviews that A Reverie has a dedicated following, with visitors returning again and again, captivated by the dining experience they offer.

### Utilizing Visual Content

Customer-provided photos speak volumes about the sensory experience that A Reverie offers. Images showcasing beautifully plated dishes and well-appointed tables convey the essence of fine dining—the colors, textures, and creativity of the food are evident and tantalizing. Photos of the relaxed space invite viewers to imagine themselves enjoying an exquisite meal under the softly glowing lights of the restaurant.

### Final Thoughts

In conclusion, A Reverie stands out as a gem in the heart of Goa’s culinary scene. With its stellar rating and accolades, this restaurant promises an escape into a world of flavor, creativity, and aesthetic beauty. Whether you’re a local or just visiting, this is one dining experience that should not be missed.
